        "content": "<p>My notes are here, but ATM the material on Kan extensions in them stops right after I show how to visualize what the formula above \"means\" (in section 7.11).<br>\n<a href=\"http://angg.twu.net/LATEX/2020favorite-conventions.pdf\">http://angg.twu.net/LATEX/2020favorite-conventions.pdf</a></p>",
