    {
        "content": "<p>You might be interested in the co/end approach to this - in particular you can write the limit formula you gave as an end, and there's a very short (although not necessarily enlightening) proof that this formula is correct using co/end calculus. See e.g. Proposition 2.3.5 in Fosco Loregian's book (<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/1501.02503.pdf\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/1501.02503.pdf</a>)</p>",
